fr.univ_tours.li.mdjedaini.ideb.eval.metric

Class MetricIterativeCommonMeasure

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.univ_tours.li.mdjedaini.ideb.eval.metric.Metric
      • fr.univ_tours.li.mdjedaini.ideb.eval.metric.MetricIterativeCommonMeasure

  • public class MetricIterativeCommonMeasure
extends Metric
    This metric evaluates the evolution of the access area. Access area is defined as all the primary cells (tuples) accessed. It evaluates how rich is the access area provided by the SUT.
